s 2018 drama film Leave No Trace. After supporting roles in the 2019 films The King, Jojo Rabbit and True History of the Kelly Gang, as well as the 2021 thriller Old, Edgar Wright's psychological horror film Last Night in Soho established her as one of the industry's lead actresses.","name":"Thomasin McKenzie","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"GR","iso_639_1":"el","name":"ελληνικά","english_name":"Greek","data":{"biography":"Η Τομαζίν Μακέντζι (Thomasin McKenzie) είναι ηθοποιός από τη Νέα Ζηλανδία. Μετά από ένα μικρό ρόλο στο The Hobbit: The Battle of Five Armies, ανέβηκε στην κορυφή της κριτικής με τον πρωταγωνιστικό ρόλο στην δραματική ταινία Leave No Trace της Debra Granik το 2018. Μετά από δεύτερους ρόλους στις ταινίες του 2019 The King, Jojo Rabbit και True History of the Kelly Gang, καθώς και στο θρίλερ Old του 2021, η ταινία ψυχολογικού τρόμου Last Night in Soho του Edgar Wright την καθιέρωσε ως μία από τις κορυφαίες ηθοποιούς του κλάδου.","name":"Τομαζίν Μακέντζι","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"Thomasin McKenzie (* 26. Juli 2000 in Wellington) ist eine neuseeländische Schauspielerin.\n\nIn dem 2012 veröffentlichten Filmdrama Existence von Juliet Bergh erhielt McKenzie ihre erste Filmrolle. Im Jahr 2015 erhielt McKenzie in der neuseeländischen Soap Shortland Street ihre erste Fernsehrolle und spielte darin Pixie Hannah. Ihre erste Hauptrolle in einem Film erhielt sie 2018 an der Seite von Ben Foster in Leave No Trace von Debra Granik. Ben Foster spielt im Film ihren Vater.\n\nHiernach erhielt sie Rollen als Philippa von England in dem Filmdrama The King von David Michôd sowie als verfolgte Jüdin im Nationalsozialismus in der Tragikomödie Jojo Rabbit von Taika Waititi.\n\nQuelle: Wikipedia","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"ES","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"Thomasin Harcourt Mckenzie (26 de julio de 2000) es una actriz neozelandesa.​ Es más conocida por su papel en la película estadounidense de 2018 Leave No Trace, con la cual recibió aprobación de la crítica.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"토마신 맥켄지","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"Новозеландская актриса, получившая мировое признание после выхода на экраны драмы «Не оставляй следов». На фестивале «Сандэнс» Маккензи была отмечена как одна из пяти многообещающих звёзд фестиваля.\n\nТомасин Харкорт Маккензи родилась в 2000 году в семье актрисы и режиссёра. Её младшая сестра Давида и старший брат Питер также стали актёрами. В 2018 году окончила Университетскую школу им. Сэмюэля Марсдена.","name":"Томасин МакКензи","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"BR","iso_639_1":"pt","name":"Português","english_name":"Portuguese","data":{"biography":"Thomasin \"Tom\" McKenzie (nascido em julho de 2000) é uma atriz neozelandesa. Mais conhecida por interpretar Pixie Hannah em Shortland Street, ela também estrelou em O Hobbit: A Batalha dos Cinco Exércitos como Astrid, em Lucy Lewis Não Pode Perder como Lucy Lewis e na série web Bright Summer Night como Petra Quince, tendo o papel principal no filme Leave No Trace (2018) e Jojo Rabbit (2019).","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"MX","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"Thomasin Harcourt Mckenzie (26 de julio de 2000) es una actriz neozelandesa.​ Es más conocida por su papel en la película estadounidense de 2018 Leave No Trace, con la cual recibió aprobación de la crítica.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"トーマシン・マッケンジー","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"新西兰演员","name":"托马辛·麦肯齐","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"紐西蘭演員","name":"託馬辛·麥肯齊","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Томасін МакКензі","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IR","iso_639_1":"fa","name":"فارسی","english_name":"Persian","data":{"biography":"","name":"توماسین مکنزی","primary":false}}]}},"person_2539_translations":{"at":1773319438053,"data":{"id":2539,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Julie Dreyfus (born January 24, 1966 in Paris) is a French actress.\n\nDreyfus, who speaks fluent Japanese, French, and English, is well known in Japan, where she made her TV debut on a French-language lesson program on NHK's educational channel in the late 1980s, and has appeared on the TV show Ryōri no Tetsujin (Iron Chef) as a guest and judge. She is best known to Western audiences for the role of Sofie Fatale in the film Kill Bill Vol. 1 and has been associated with Quentin Tarantino, who is a good friend.","name":"Julie Dreyfus","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"Julie Dreyfus (geboren am 24. Januar 1966 in Paris) ist eine französische Schauspielerin.\n\nDreyfus, die fließend Japanisch, Französisch und Englisch spricht, ist in Japan bekannt, wo sie Ende der 1980er Jahre ihr Fernsehdebüt in einer französischsprachigen Unterrichtssendung des Bildungssenders NHK gab und in der Fernsehsendung Ryōri no Tetsujin auftrat (Iron Chef) als Gast Juror.  Dem westlichen Publikum ist sie vor allem durch ihre Rolle als Sofie Fatale im Film \"Kill Bill Vol. 1\" bekannt. Sie wurde mit Quentin Tarantino in Verbindung gebracht, der ein guter Freund ist.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"줄리 드레이퍼스","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"朱莉·德雷福斯（Julie Dreyfus，1966年1月24日出生于巴黎）是法国女演员。","name":"朱莉·德雷福斯","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"ジュリー・ドレフュス","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Жулі Дрейфус","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"朱莉·德賴弗斯（Julie Dreyfus，1966 年 1 月 24 日出生於巴黎）是法國女演員。","name":"朱莉·德賴弗斯","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"Julie Dreyfus (née le 24 janvier 1966 à Paris) est une actrice française.\n\nParlant couramment le japonais, le français et l'anglais, elle est très connue au Japon, où elle a fait ses débuts à la télévision dans une émission d'apprentissage du français sur la chaîne éducative NHK à la fin des années 1980, et où elle est apparue dans l'émission Ryōri no Tetsujin (Iron Chef) en tant qu'invitée et juge. Elle est surtout connue du public occidental pour son rôle de Sofie Fatale dans le film Kill Bill Vol. 1 et est associée à Quentin Tarantino.","name":"","primary":false}}]}},"person_3156248_translations":{"at":1773384111857,"data":{"id":3156248,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Lee Gregory Jagow was born on September 13, 1951 in Beaver Dam, Wisconsin, USA. He was an actor, known for Infamous Crime Scenes: John Lennon (2022), Infamous Crime Scenes: JFK (2022) and The Presidents: Obama (2022). He died on February 10, 2023 in Aurora, Illinois, USA.","name":"Lee Jagow","primary":true}}]}},"movie_1451867_credits":{"at":177